---
---

<section class="editorial-section">
  <div class="container editorial-inner">
    <div class="editorial-text flex-column">
      <span class="eyebrow">Nuestra filosofía</span>
      <h2 class="editorial-title">Menos es más.<br />Pero tiene que ser bueno.</h2>
      <p class="editorial-body">
        Diseñamos ropa interior para hombres que no quieren pensar en ropa interior.
        Sin adornos innecesarios, sin marcas llamativas. Solo microfibra de primera calidad,
        cortes que no se mueven y una durabilidad que justifica cada peso.
      </p>
      <ul class="editorial-points flex-column">
        <li class="flex-row"><i class="bi bi-check2"></i> Microfibra 100%</li>
        <li class="flex-row"><i class="bi bi-check2"></i> Sin costuras internas irritantes</li>
        <li class="flex-row"><i class="bi bi-check2"></i> Elástico de alta durabilidad</li>
        <li class="flex-row"><i class="bi bi-check2"></i> Lavable a máquina, retiene la forma</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="editorial-visual" aria-hidden="true">
      <img src="/img/logo-stamp.avif" alt="" class="editorial-logo" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .editorial-section {
    background: var(--bone-50);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 80px 0;
  }

  .editorial-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 48px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .editorial-text {
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--carbon-300);
  }

  .editorial-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 52px);
    line-height: 0.95;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--carbon-900);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .editorial-body {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--carbon-500);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 480px;
  }

  .editorial-points {
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 10px;
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .editorial-points li {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--carbon-700);
    gap: 10px;
    justify-content: flex-start;
  }

  .editorial-points .bi-check2 {
    color: var(--carbon-900);
    font-size: 16px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .editorial-visual {
    display: none;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #EBE3D2 25%, #D9CFB9 25%, #D9CFB9 50%, #EBE3D2 50%, #EBE3D2 75%, #D9CFB9 75%);
    background-size: 36px 36px;
    border: 2px solid var(--carbon-900);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-press);
  }

  .editorial-logo {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    object-fit: contain;
    padding: 32px;
  }

  @media (min-width: 750px) {
    .editorial-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }

    .editorial-visual {
      display: block;
    }
  }
</style>
